</div>
<p id="p-22">Immune response had no effect on mean waking activity (Complete 4-way ANOVA genotype:ru <i>F</i><sub>2,23976</sub> = 21.96, <i>p</i> &lt; 0.00001, GS1.32 &gt; PGRP-Lca vs. GS1.32/+: <i>F</i><sub>1,16632</sub> = 0.49, <i>p</i> = 0.4858, GS1.32 &gt; PGRP-Lca vs. +/PGRP-Lca: <i>F</i><sub>1,15840</sub> = 39.18, <i>p</i> &lt; 0.00001). See <a class="xref xref-fig" href="#fig-4" data-jats-ref-type="fig" data-jats-rid="fig-4">Figs. 4</a> and <a class="xref xref-fig" href="#fig-5" data-jats-ref-type="fig" data-jats-rid="fig-5">5</a>. <a class="xref xref-table" href="#table-2" data-jats-ref-type="table" data-jats-rid="table-2">Table 2</a> gives the means and standard errors for mean waking activity.</p>
